============ 制作nginx的deb包 ============
下载源码
mkdir src
cd src
apt-get source nginx

安装依赖
apt-get build-dep nginx dh-make
apt-get install build-essential fakeroot

mkdir build
cd build
wget nginx-1.4.6.tar.gz
tar xf nginx-1.4.6.tar.gz
cd nginx-1.4.6
dh_make -s -e your-email -f ../nginx-1.4.6.tar.gz
编辑debian/control debian/rules debian/changelog文件
如果需要覆盖默认的configure,增加make任务:
override_dh_auto_configure

dpkg-buildpackage -rfakeroot h或 dpkg-buildpackage -uc -us
修改源码之后 需要dpkg-source --commit提交补丁


可以:"dpkg -x nginx_1.4.6-1_amd64.deb . "看结果

nginx -V 看当前配置 
nginx -t 测试配置文件



===============
debian/package.upstart
If this exists, it is installed into etc/init/package.conf in the
package build directory.

debian/package.init
Otherwise, if this exists, it is installed into etc/init.d/package
in the package build directory. 
